createQuery

<T> Query<T> createQuery(EntityCriteria<T> criteria,
                         ReadStrategy strategy)
Creates a store-specific Query object using a Criteria The store is not immediately consult for results. The consult only occurs when one the Query methods is invoked. Repeated invocations of the same query method may return different results as data in the store is updated.

Type Parameters:
T - return object type
Parameters:
criteria - filter to be applied to the bulk data
ReadStrategy - read strategy
